        "translations": {
          "en": "Ahmad ibn Harun al-Fami (may God be pleased with him) narrated to us. He said: Muhammad ibn Abdullah ibn Ja'far narrated to us, from his father, from Muhammad ibn Abd al-Jabbar, from Abd al-Rahman ibn Abi Najran, from al-Hasan ibn Ali ibn Ribat, from Abu Bakr al-Hadrami, who said: Al-Sadiq Ja'far ibn Muhammad (peace be upon them both) said:",
